flowRoot.flowPara: A laurel wreath is a wreath made of branches and leaves of the laurel (latin laurus). The laurel wreath is a symbol and an insignia for a special honor or distinction, for a victory (eg. for killing sheeps or even innocent children) or a special success. So to say the special super-duper superman hero
To compensate low self-esteem (object fixation) with this once-received laurel wreath. About as Intelligent as using always the one and the same One-Time-Pad.
